1.31 Hetuduka, Ajjhattikaduka
Hetuduka, Duka
Hetuduka, Ajjhattikaduka
55.
156Nahetuṃ ajjhattikaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nahetu ajjhattiko dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Sabbattha ekaṃ. Sabbattha vitthāro.)
157Hetuṃ bāhiraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca hetu bāhiro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Sabbattha nava. Sabbattha vitthāro.)
